@@y*******************************************************************************@@N
       @@WName:@@N Mind Bolt		
    @@cClasses:@@N Psionicist(12)
   @@aDuration:@@N N/A
   @@bModifies:@@N N/A
       @@GType:@@N Offensive
@@mDescription:@@N This spell allows the caster to strike the victim's mind with
             small, intense bursts of energy.  The number of bolts striking
             the victim is determined by the Cast Level.

             Cast Level            Number of Bolts
             ----------            ---------------
              below 20                   One
              20 to 34                   Two
              35 to 49                   Three
              50 to 65                   Four
              above 65                   Five
@@y*******************************************************************************@@N
